{"tid":92652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［負能量收集區］入黎放負啦！","createTime":"2017-01-23T17:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T20:22:23.000Z","uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8994eba2888891cafc24654bfaf0a3dcb171673d","tid":92652,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"我先！<br />\n本來有個好想實踐到既夢想 <br />\n但呢排已經比現實迫左我放棄<br />\n生存充滿限制 唔容許理想 你估你可以天真任性到幾多年？<br />\n咁努力咁堅持都冇用 都係唔會做到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係做個浮浮沈沈 見步行步 求求其其搵餐飯食既廢青算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最好笑係連呢個諗法都比人質疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地問我：你咁廢你肯定真係可以搵到餐飽飯食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地既諗法本來唔重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但最可悲既係連自己都認同自己係地底泥 永無番身之日就gg了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a54b04028a040cc6d283609c9fffa74f5c546a1","tid":92652,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d9a16634c7a35b51c24f562f231b11b0ca99f6","tid":92652,"uid":2266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"人生無希望"},{"pid":"ad26c26537eb255aaed1473432395c84c2a32013","tid":92652,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生無希望</blockquote><br />\nMore"},{"pid":"4cac03839578b2202c297dec293ab9959466de12","tid":92652,"uid":59148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:24:56.000Z","msg":"好驚對個SP沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdade75d440532c6f1f5216131591b7ba1fd3f97","tid":92652,"uid":2266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人生無希望</blockquote><br />\nMore</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc467db31aa2c5d46af30e011a9664b8a83607","tid":92652,"uid":2266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好驚對個SP沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地當你肉便器炸<br />\n咪玩過界啦你"},{"pid":"9654c5446ab93b777ac1549a458a8848705b9770","tid":92652,"uid":59148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好驚對個SP沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地當你肉便器炸<br />\n咪玩過界啦你</blockquote><br />\n佢口話唔係當我純sp... <br />\n我心底或多或少都知係點<br />\n但我地又會好似普通朋友咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564cd1fc74465a0db6acaeb3368265174ab864f4","tid":92652,"uid":6285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:52:13.000Z","msg":"到底我做錯啲咩？<br />\n雖然你不停話我冇做錯 但你話你好大壓力<br />\n但啲壓力係你俾自己嘅 你都識講 我冇俾過你<br />\n到底我做錯啲咩？導致你有壓力 而要承擔後果嗰個係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解講咗成晚 你不停話好大壓力 唔知點解決<br />\n我叫你放棄生活上一啲嘢 因為你太忙handle唔到先搞到自己咁大壓力<br />\n你話可以放棄咩 朋友你又唔想放棄 工作你又唔想放棄 咁唔通放棄屋企人？<br />\n<br />\n咁你唯有放棄我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咁講又話我發悔氣<br />\n我真係唔知點先幫到你<br />\n你雖然冇直接講 但你都講過朋友喺你心目中重要過女朋友好多<br />\n咁你唔放棄我仲可以放棄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係唔明當初點解你要追我 到底追我返嚟係想要啲咩？講到對每段關係都好認真，但一有壓力嘅時候，覺得最可以放棄嘅係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我走 追都冇追 留都冇留 搵都冇搵<br />\n<br />\n雖然一齊時間唔耐 我知你之前嘅經歷都令到你好保護自己有啲封閉<br />\n但我都有自己以前嘅經歷 我都俾人hurt過好多次<br />\n但到底我係做錯啲乜嘢？點解你同再對上一個都要同我講我好好 係你地唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁到底我係做錯乜嘢 先令到我冇一段好嘅愛情？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aec0018b811cfb27cae86e9acd2c7c482d7bcb6","tid":92652,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好驚對個SP沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地當你肉便器炸<br />\n咪玩過界啦你</blockquote><br />\n佢口話唔係當我純sp... <br />\n我心底或多或少都知係點<br />\n但我地又會好似普通朋友咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁口一定話唔係淨係當你sp先令你更有動力繼續做佢sp ge<br />\n正正常常搵過個啦 <br />\n我始終覺得sp同伴侶分唔開會搞到關係好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d6be7e373a1e09e061cd713171dc0b0093e36e","tid":92652,"uid":59148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n人地當你肉便器炸<br />\n咪玩過界啦你</blockquote><br />\n佢口話唔係當我純sp... <br />\n我心底或多或少都知係點<br />\n但我地又會好似普通朋友咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁口一定話唔係淨係當你sp先令你更有動力繼續做佢sp ge<br />\n正正常常搵過個啦 <br />\n我始終覺得sp同伴侶分唔開會搞到關係好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同佢都唔鍾意比名份綁住 所以一直都無承認過大家既身分<br />\n我自己都唔想拍拖 <br />\n呢種關係可能係好 但仲未調整到自己心態<br />\n只係發現原來自己會在乎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e3ba1788d6d3f5d2429e57ca2ed3ca0f0075f2","tid":92652,"uid":77388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底我做錯啲咩？<br />\n雖然你不停話我冇做錯 但你話你好大壓力<br />\n但啲壓力係你俾自己嘅 你都識講 我冇俾過你<br />\n到底我做錯啲咩？導致你有壓力 而要承擔後果嗰個係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解講咗成晚 你不停話好大壓力 唔知點解決<br />\n我叫你放